<H1>debian-announce Mailing List Subscription</H1>

debian-announce is a moderated mailing list which is used to broadcast
announcements of general interest to the Debian community.
As all the announcements also go into the News section of our web pages
it is also useful for people who like to keep abreast of changes in
the Debian pages.

<P>To subscribe to debian-announce you can follow the instructions at
<a href="http://www.debian.org/MailingLists/subscribe">http://www.debian.org/MailingLists/subscribe</a>
or you can simply use the automatic subscription form below.
As part of the subscription process you will be sent mail which you must
reply to to finish subscribing. This is a security measure to keep people
from subscribing others to the lists without their permission.

<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/subscribe.pl">

<INPUT type=hidden name="subscribe" value="debian-announce">

<STRONG>Your E-Mail address:</STRONG>
<BR><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="user_email" SIZE="50"><BR>
<INPUT TYPE="SUBMIT"> <INPUT TYPE="RESET">
</FORM>

